[SPEAKER_00] Ako ja nisam čovjek od denutka za čeća, kad ja postajem čovjek?

220
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovi neki tupavci kažu rođenjem.

221
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

222
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ove snike su mi interesantne.

223
00:13:16,000 --> 00:13:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta mislite šta je ovo?

224
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su Nilsonove fotografije jednog nizozemca koji je posljednom tehnikom ultrazvuka pratio trudnoću žene.

225
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ova velika kugla je ženska spolna stanica.

226
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon ovulacije.

227
00:13:30,000 --> 00:13:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] A oni malci od muža.

228
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

229
00:13:36,000 --> 00:13:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta se dešava?

230
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ću govoriti o bračnom činu.

231
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] I muškarac polaže sjeme u ženu.

232
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Oko dva miliona.

233
00:13:49,000 --> 00:13:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Od tih dva miliona navale na onu jednu.

234
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] A šta se dešava?

235
00:13:59,000 --> 00:14:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Do ženske spolne stanice će doći koji?

236
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najbrži.

237
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najjači.

238
00:14:05,000 --> 00:14:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najspretniji.

239
00:14:07,000 --> 00:14:09,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najsposobniji.

240
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Najlukaviji.

241
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer tako?

242
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] I taj će ući u stanicu.

243
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jer to je prirodna selekcija.

244
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono ću vam reći.

245
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kod ovih medicinskih potpornih tehnika toga nema.

246
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:30,000
[SPEAKER_00] da je pričnih bira jednoga koji mu se sviđa.

247
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema odabira.

248
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo kako je Bog zamislio.

249
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,000
[SPEAKER_00] Već prvi problem.

250
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

251
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] A vratim još natrag.

252
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo što vidite.

253
00:14:42,000 --> 00:14:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] U ženskoj spolne stanici je jezgra.

254
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koja ima 23 kromosoma.

255
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:52,000
[SPEAKER_00] Iz muške spolne stanice dolazi od drugih jezgra, sa drugih 23.

256
00:14:52,000 --> 00:14:55,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dolazi do spaljanja tih dvih jezgri u jednu.

257
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:58,000
