265
00:15:24,000 --> 00:15:27,000
[SPEAKER_00] Jesu li to dvije stanice?

266
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ili je to novi čovjek?

267
00:15:29,000 --> 00:15:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imam li ja pravo s tim raspolagati kako hoću?

268
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imam ili nemam?

269
00:15:39,000 --> 00:15:43,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

270
00:15:43,000 --> 00:15:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prvih osam dana putujemo kroz jajavod.

271
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dijelimo se 2, 4, 8, 16, 32, 64, 128, ajmo dalje.

272
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] I dolazimo u maternicu i tu dolazi nidacija.

273
00:15:59,000 --> 00:16:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je drugi ključni faktor.

274
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Prvi je začeće, drugi je nidacija.

275
00:16:04,000 --> 00:16:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Šta radi spirala i šta radi hormonalne pilule u Hrvatskoj?

276
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] One spriječavaju nidaciju.

277
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su sredstva sa abortivnim učinkom.

278
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:20,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nema u Hrvatskoj kontraceptivnih pilula.

279
00:16:20,000 --> 00:16:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] To ćemo odmah reći.

280
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] To su zablude.

281
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na crkvu, spriječavanje nidacije je abortivni učinak.

282
00:16:29,000 --> 00:16:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] Na crkvu je to abortivni učinak. To je ubojstvo čovjeka.

283
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Koji je star 8 do 10 dana.

284
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što god neko misli o tome.

285
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nek mi dokaže suprotno.

286
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:45,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

287
00:16:45,000 --> 00:16:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovako smo izgledali nakon mjesec dana.

288
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:52,000
