289
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] A vi ste već ovaki.

290
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo u sredini je srce koje kuca i dan danas u vama.

291
00:16:57,000 --> 00:17:00,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kupčena vrpca je razvijena.

292
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Krivo tog se razvija.

293
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

294
00:17:03,000 --> 00:17:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon dva mjeseca.

295
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je osnov tjedana.

296
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo oči, uši, usta, nos, ruke.

297
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sve potpuno oblikovano.

298
00:17:13,000 --> 00:17:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo još nije vrijeme kad se rade pobačaj.

299
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:21,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

300
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pobačaj se radi kad ovako izgledamo.

301
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,000
[SPEAKER_00] Kad će imamo mozak.

302
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:28,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je 12. tjedan.

303
00:17:30,000 --> 00:17:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Možeš li neko reći ne ubi.

304
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:33,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne ubi.

305
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:35,000
[UNKNOWN] Zvoli.

306
00:17:37,000 --> 00:17:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ali moraš znati ko bila si to.

307
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

308
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:46,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ovo je već šesti mjesec.

309
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

310
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:49,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sedmi, osmi.

311
00:17:49,000 --> 00:17:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] Rodi se beba.

312
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:53,000
[SPEAKER_00] Pišo linko.

313
00:17:53,000 --> 00:17:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

314
00:17:56,000 --> 00:17:57,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je uvjerenje crkve.

315
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je uvjerenje crkve.

316
00:17:58,000 --> 00:18:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da ono što je ljudsko ne samo da je prihvaćeno i poštilo od vjere.

317
00:18:01,000 --> 00:18:04,000
[SPEAKER_00] Već je on je također pročišćeno uzivu savršeno.

318
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je stvorio svakog čovjeka na svoju sliku.

319
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] I poleći od sveogljeg dviju dimenzija, ljudske i božanske,

320
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] bolje se razumije razlog nepovredljive vrijednosti čovjeka.

321
00:18:14,000 --> 00:18:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

322
00:18:17,000 --> 00:18:19,000
[SPEAKER_00] Dvije dimenzije života, naravno i nadnaravno,

323
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:22,000
[SPEAKER_00] omogućuju također da se bolje shvati u kojem smislu čini,

324
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:24,000
[SPEAKER_00] koji dopušta ljudskom bići da dođu na život,

325
00:18:24,000 --> 00:18:29,000
[SPEAKER_00] kojima se muž i žena uzravno daruju, su ocije trojstvene ljubavi.

326
00:18:29,000 --> 00:18:32,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sedaj to kažemo da je to nešto sveto.

327
00:18:32,000 --> 00:18:36,000
[SPEAKER_00] Bračni čin je svet u braku.

328
00:18:36,000 --> 00:18:38,000
[SPEAKER_00] Tu je Bog na dijelu.

329
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:42,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je čin iz kojeg nastaje život.

330
00:18:42,000 --> 00:18:44,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ne uvijek nastaje.

331
00:18:46,000 --> 00:18:48,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ajmo dalje.

332
00:18:48,000 --> 00:18:51,000
[SPEAKER_00] I crkva ocijenjući etičku vrijednost nekih rezultata skorašnjih

333
00:18:51,000 --> 00:18:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] i zaština medicine, što se odnese na čovjeka i njegove početke,

334
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] ne intervenira u područje vlastno-medicijskoj znanosti kao tako je,

335
00:18:58,000 --> 00:19:02,000
[SPEAKER_00] ali poziva sve zainteresirane na etičku i socijalnu odgovornost

336
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:03,000
[SPEAKER_00] za njihovo dijelo.

337
00:19:03,000 --> 00:19:05,000
[SPEAKER_00] Idemo dalje.

338
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:07,000
[SPEAKER_00] E, sad dolazimo do ovoga.

339
00:19:07,000 --> 00:19:11,000
[SPEAKER_00] Što je onda medicinski platform za čeće?

340
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] U širem smislu,

341
00:19:14,000 --> 00:19:17,000
